Package: RNAPeaks
Title: Visualize RNA-Binding Protein Peaks on Gene Structures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates quality visualizations of RNA-binding protein
    (RBP) peaks overlaid on gene structures. Supports single-gene plots,
    multi-gene genomic region plots, and integrates with GTF annotations
    from Ensembl via AnnotationHub.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
